<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Home</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/4.1.1/animate.min.css" />
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
    }
    .quote-card {
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .quote-text {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
    .quote-author {
      font-style: italic;
      text-align: right;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/navbar.ejs') %>

  <div class="container mt-5">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4">Welcome to the Home Page</h1>
    <p class="text-center text-muted mb-5">Get inspired with these motivational quotes.</p>

    <div class="row g-4">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="quote-card bg-primary animate__animated animate__fadeInLeft">
          <div class="quote-text">
            "The best way to get started is to quit talking and begin doing."
          </div>
          <div class="quote-author">– Walt Disney</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="quote-card bg-success animate__animated animate__fadeInRight">
          <div class="quote-text">
            "Don’t let yesterday take up too much of today."
          </div>
          <div class="quote-author">– Will Rogers</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="quote-card bg-warning text-dark animate__animated animate__fadeInLeft">
          <div class="quote-text">
            "It’s not whether you get knocked down, it’s whether you get up."
          </div>
          <div class="quote-author">– Vince Lombardi</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="quote-card bg-danger animate__animated animate__fadeInRight">
          <div class="quote-text">
            "The harder you work for something, the greater you’ll feel when you achieve it."
          </div>
          <div class="quote-author">– Unknown</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="quote-card bg-info text-dark animate__animated animate__fadeInLeft">
          <div class="quote-text">
            "Push yourself, because no one else is going to do it for you."
          </div>
          <div class="quote-author">– Unknown</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="quote-card bg-dark animate__animated animate__fadeInRight">
          <div class="quote-text">
            "Success doesn’t just find you. You have to go out and get it."
          </div>
          <div class="quote-author">– Unknown</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
